<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>ssham: Secure Shell Access Manager</title><link>https://ssham.pacoorozco.info/installation/</link><description>Recent content on ssham: Secure Shell Access Manager</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ssham.pacoorozco.info/installation/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Laravel Sail</title><link>https://ssham.pacoorozco.info/installation/laravel-sail/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Mar 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ssham.pacoorozco.info/installation/laravel-sail/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a
 class="gdoc-markdown__link"
 href="https://laravel.com/docs/9.x/sail"
&gt;Laravel Sail&lt;/a&gt; is a light-weight command-line interface for interacting with
Laravel&amp;rsquo;s default Docker development environment. This will create several containers to implement all SSHAM needs. An
application server and a database server.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prior to this installation, you &lt;strong&gt;need to have installed&lt;/strong&gt; this software:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a
 class="gdoc-markdown__link"
 href="https://www.docker.com/"
&gt;Docker&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clone the repository locally&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-Shell" data-lang="Shell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;git clone https://github.com/pacoorozco/ssham.git ssham
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cd ssham
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Copy &lt;a
 class="gdoc-markdown__link--code"
 href=".env.example"
&gt;&lt;code&gt;.env.example&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;code&gt;.env&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NOTE&lt;/strong&gt;: You don&amp;rsquo;t need to touch anything from this file. It works with default settings.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Manual</title><link>https://ssham.pacoorozco.info/installation/manual/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Mar 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ssham.pacoorozco.info/installation/manual/</guid><description>&lt;div class="flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap"&gt;
 &lt;h2 id="manual-installation"
 &gt;
 Manual installation
 &lt;/h2&gt;
 &lt;a data-clipboard-text="https://ssham.pacoorozco.info/installation/manual/#manual-installation" class="gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center" title="Anchor to: Manual installation" aria-label="Anchor to: Manual installation" href="#manual-installation"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="gdoc-icon gdoc_link"&gt;&lt;use xlink:href="#gdoc_link"&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clone the repository locally&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-Shell" data-lang="Shell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;git clone https://github.com/pacoorozco/ssham.git ssham
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cd ssham
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Install PHP dependencies with &lt;a
 class="gdoc-markdown__link"
 href="http://getcomposer.org"
&gt;composer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-Shell" data-lang="Shell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;curl -s https://getcomposer.org/installer | php
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;php composer.phar install
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Copy &lt;a
 class="gdoc-markdown__link--code"
 href=".env.example"
&gt;&lt;code&gt;.env.example&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;code&gt;.env&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Modify the content of the &lt;code&gt;.env&lt;/code&gt; file to put your settings, something like that:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;DB_HOST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Your database host&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;DB_DATABASE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Your database name&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;DB_USERNAME&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Your database user&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;DB_PASSWORD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Your database password&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Seed database in order to play with some data&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>